summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty Freee.l.f. Cosmetics' Camo Liquid Bronzer & Contour is a lightweight, pigment-packed liquid bronzer and contour hybrid that gives you a long-lasting bronze and blends out into a natural-looking finish. The rounded, grooved applicator makes it so easy to add gorgeous definition to your makeup look.

how_to_use: Dab 1-2 dots on hollows of cheeks, forehead, sides of nose and jawline.Blend out using e.l.f.'s Liquid Bronzer & Contour Duo Brush (sold separately).

reviews.headline: Blends Seamlessly
reviews.comments: I got the fair color for my skin and it was my first time using contour. This product blended seamlessly into my makeup and created a light natural toned look to my face. Perfect for a no-makeup makeup look. I used two dots at every section of my face (cheeks, jaw, nose, forehead).

reviews.headline: Cool Tones
reviews.comments: I have very fair skin, this is one of the few contour products I've found that is a very cool brown

reviews.headline: Pleasantly surprised
reviews.comments: I tried this with very low expectations as I am usually disappointed when trying new products, hoping something will surprise me eventually. This is actually a wonderful product and at the price point, can not be beat. It blends well (I use with Tarte Shape Tape foundation) and stays put. Its very pigmented and you dont need to use a ton. The finish is so pretty that id use it all over if there were lighter colors that could be used as a foundation. This will be replacing my other contour products that I held onto because I couldnt find anything else. Just goes to show that more expensive prodcuts arent always better.

reviews.headline: Easy to apply
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] blends nicely. Easy to apply. I would maybe pick a different color but obviously thats a subjective issue. The product itself was really nice

reviews.headline: This is a great bronzer and I would buy it again

reviews.headline: Love it
reviews.comments: Really impressed with the e.l.f. liquid bronzer and contour! The texture is smooth and blends easily without patchiness. It gives a natural, sculpted look and feels super lightweight on the skin. Great pigment, no harsh lines, and it stays put all day. Plus, you can't beat the price!

reviews.headline: Doesn't blend well
reviews.comments: The color is amazing but it's a sticky substance. It doesn't blend well. I've tried different brushes and beauty blenders it's still blotchy. I wish I could love it but the formula isn't for me.

reviews.headline: Broke me out, I'm devastated
reviews.comments: Love the color, love the packaging, love the price, omg, this could have been the PERFECT product, the shade range, everything is wonderful. EXCEPT , it broke me out. I've been doing extractions for the past two months....singled everything else out that might be causing it (even though...from the places on my face where I was breaking out, it was already kind of obvious lol) and deduced something in this product gives me really, really clogged pores. It's odd....the blushes don't do that. Oh well.....have to keep looking for my new contour.

faceoff_positive.comments: I this product a couple of days ago after applying for this product through BZZAgent in which I received the product in exchange for an honest review. I have used many different cream contours but never a liquid and I will 100% be using this liquid bronzer in the future. Although the shade was too dark for my skin tone (shade 11) it still went on effortlessly and blended so well. The benefits to this product are the fact that my bronzer will take way less time to apply in the future. I love the thick applicator and that you can put on minimal product. I am going to buy this product in my correct shade asap. I am forsure going to recommend this product to my friends and family. It went on so effortlessly and even though it was the wrong shade I was able to blend it out enough so I could still wear it. I have a hard time with my makeup separating and did not have that problem with this product at all! Highly recommend.
faceoff_positive.headline: Super Blendable and natural finish!

faceoff_negative.comments: I was hoping elf was gonna come with  contours but this is just a bronzer unfortunately. I got 2 shades med 5 and tan 6. Hoping one would give contour unfortunately no.  My skin looks better with contour and blush. So I was hoping for a nice cool toned shade to build those shadows. These just end up looking like I used bronzer to try and contour the shades are too warm. Even though they don't work as a contour they are a nice formula, feel good on the skin and have good staying power.  I have been using elf products for over 30 yrs and they have come a long way so hoping they come through with some true cool toned contour shaded.
faceoff_negative.headline: Not a contour
